flowchart TD
  A[Ticket Received] --> B[Classify Severity]
  B --> C{Critical?}
  C -- Yes --> D[Page On-Call Engineer]
  C -- No --> E[Assign Support Agent]
  D --> F[Open Incident Channel]
  E --> G[Gather Reproduction Steps]
  F --> H[Apply Hotfix]
  G --> I[Route to Product Team]
  H --> J[Close Incident]
  I --> J[Close Ticket]
